----------------------                  ----------------------
---------------------- How to use files ----------------------
----------------------                  ----------------------

For Node-Red JSON file upload it to your Node-Red app by using "import" section and choosing the file. 
To create databases in your SQL sever, copy and paste the content of "db_creation.txt" and past it into as querry.
For Grafana dashboard template, upload it in the same ways as Node-Red JSON file.
